
'''''Something Necessary''''' ni film yikinamico yo muri [[Kenya]] yasohotse 2013 iyobowe na Judy Kibinge . Yerekanwe mu gice cya Sinema y'isi muri iki gihe mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Toronto 2013 .  

== Umugambi ==
[[Kenya]] 2007: Nyuma y'ibyavuye mu matora ya perezida atavugwaho rumwe, urugomo rwadutse. Agatsiko k'urubyiruko rudafite akazi rwatewe n'abanyapolitiki bajya mu mihanda hirya no hino.

Anne akanguka mu bitaro avuye muri koma asanga ubuzima yagize mbere yihohoterwa butakibaho. Umugabo we yarapfuye kandi yashyinguwe mbere yuko agira amahirwe yo kumuririra. Umuhungu we Kitur ari muri koma kandi The Haven, umurima we n'inzu, byangijwe kandi byarasahuwe. Yagiye kuba umuforomo,  umugore aba umupfakazi udafite akazi n'umuhungu uri mu bitaro uharanira kubaka umurima we.

Ikirenze ibyo, ni umugore wa Kikuyu utuye mu gace ka  Kalenjin, mushiki we yemera ko adahari kandi ko agomba gusubira mu rugo kugira ngo abe mu bwoko bwe. Ariko kubijyanye na Anne, ari murugo kandi ntazemera ko hagira umuntu umutera ubwoba.

Mugihe filime yegereje, Joseph yitegereza nyina akora yibaza icyo byose bivuze. Yahisemo gusibanganya amateka ye y’urugomo maze ava mu mudugudu kugira ngo atangire ubuzima bushya i [[Nairobi]] hamwe n’umukobwa w’inzozi ze. Mugihe ibi bibaho, Anne asanga kwizera kwe kugaruwe muburyo butunguranye kubwimpano itazwi bimuha ubutwari nimbaraga akeneye cyane guhaguruka, guhangana namateka ye no gukomeza.

